title: MyMountSinai - Sign Up - Mount Sinai Health System
snippet: Please note that MyMountSinai Self Signup is only available for current Mount Sinai patients that are 18 years of age or older. Please add donotreply@mountsinai.org to your safe senders list in order to receive MyMountSinai notifications in your email.

For safety reasons, please note that three 3 incorrect password attempts will result in your account being locked, and you must contact our MyChart support line to have it unlocked – this phone number appears at the bottom of the last page of this document.
